        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Martin joins Companies House from the Welsh Government where he has spent over 25 years working in various policy roles.</p>

<p>Most recently, Martin was Deputy Director for Community Safety leading on the Welsh Governmentâ€™s approach to crime, justice, civil contingencies and emergency planning. Martin has also worked in a number of delivery roles within economic development, primarily on business development and inward investment.</p>

<p>Martin has an MBA with a focus on innovation and organisational culture. He is also a Welsh learner.</p>
</div>
